      1 c  Chocolate cookie crumbs; (15
      2 tb Butter or margarine; melted
           -----filling-----
    1/2 c  Butter or margarine; softene
    3/4 c  Sugar
      3 oz Unsweetened chocolate
      1 ts Vanilla extract
      1 ts Peppermint extract
      3    Eggs
    1/2 c  Whipping cream
