    1/4 c  Sugar
      1 ea Egg; large, beaten
      1 ts Vanilla extract
    1/4 c  Milk
    1/4 c  Cocoa
      2 c  Flour; unbleached, unsifted
      1 x  -------cocoa frosting-------
      2 tb Cocoa
